      "createdAt": "2022-11-08T10:33:02.380Z",
      "author": "ian12 (Ian Salalila)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>So the idea is to create an automated helpdesk, where incoming e-mail from the support mail box comes into <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> as an open ticket.</p>\n<p>Now for the status change (closed/working on/open) I would like to send an automated e-mail.<br />\nIs there a way to automatically fill in the “requester e-mail” column from the e-mail sender field?</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/1/16c3f3cedd69a6e81b88023579e902134bc6b61c.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/1/16c3f3cedd69a6e81b88023579e902134bc6b61c_2_690x178.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"178\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1583×410 42.6 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 103413,
      "postNumber": 2,
      "createdAt": "2022-11-08T18:26:20.563Z",
      "author": "Nir-Jetpack (Nir @ Jetpack Team)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/ian12\">@ian12</a> .<br />\n<a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/133\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Extract</a> is a marketplace app that can help you extract e-mail address of requester and save it in your board column so you can close the loop and send an auto responder.</p>\n<p>Here is a short demo</p><div class=\"youtube-onebox lazy-video-container\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZTbOd2EwNy4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n    <img class=\"youtube-thumbnail\" src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/a/3/a387af5a45b42b35594a938a972674acb563622c.jpeg\" title=\"Integrate Gmail and Outlook to monday.com -  Extract Sender name and email address to your board\" width=\"690\" height=\"388\" />\n  </a>\n</div>\n"
    },
    {
      "id": 103438,
      "postNumber": 3,
      "createdAt": "2022-11-08T22:54:58.302Z",
      "author": "BiancaT (Bianca Taylor)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hey <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/ian12\">@ian12</a>,</p>\n<p>Had you explored the emails and activities app?</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://support.monday.com/hc/en-us/articles/360019213180-Emails-Activities-on-monday-com\">Emails &amp; Activities on monday.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>You are able to log new contact names + email addresses from incoming senders when the email is received in the app:</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/6/6601b95cd463e396de2f37df63d18e8e95da7076.png\" title=\"Screen Shot 2022-11-09 at 11.53.41 am\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/6/6601b95cd463e396de2f37df63d18e8e95da7076_2_690x361.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-11-09 at 11.53.41 am\" width=\"690\" height=\"361\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">Screen Shot 2022-11-09 at 11.53.41 am</span><span class=\"informations\">860×450 32 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Let me know if this helps!</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 103601,
      "postNumber": 4,
      "createdAt": "2022-11-10T08:42:37.121Z",
      "author": "ian12 (Ian Salalila)",
      "cookedHtml": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://sea1.discourse-cdn.com/monday/user_avatar/community.monday.com/biancat/48/14133_2.png\" class=\"avatar\" /> Bianca (:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>know</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>How do I do this, I’ve tried searching in integrations, but I can not find anything</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 103689,
