      "author": "BiancaT (Bianca Taylor)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>You should find the <strong>emails and activities app</strong> via the updates section, and items view center:</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/1/1d76db487485f295bf721d7b69059c7719d923ef.png\" title=\"Screen Shot 2022-11-11 at 9.08.55 am\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/1/1d76db487485f295bf721d7b69059c7719d923ef_2_690x221.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-11-11 at 9.08.55 am\" width=\"690\" height=\"221\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">Screen Shot 2022-11-11 at 9.08.55 am</span><span class=\"informations\">1060×340 22.7 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Search for the <strong>emails + activities app</strong>:</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/6/6fb4351acd427fac04a459fc30d3d345b37cf0d3.png\" title=\"Screen Shot 2022-11-11 at 9.09.00 am\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/6/6fb4351acd427fac04a459fc30d3d345b37cf0d3_2_689x208.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-11-11 at 9.09.00 am\" width=\"689\" height=\"208\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">Screen Shot 2022-11-11 at 9.09.00 am</span><span class=\"informations\">2424×732 101 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>"
